New species of Dexosarcophaga Townsend from Panama with an illustrated key to species of the subgenus Bezzisca (Diptera: Sarcophagidae)A new species belonging to the subgenus Bezzisca of the Neotropical genus Dexosarcophaga is described. Dexosarcophaga (Bezzisca) bermudezi sp. nov. is described from Panama and represents the sixteenth species of this subgenus. An illustrated key to identifying the Bezzisca species is also provided.